com.g6pay.sdk
Class G6Pay

java.lang.Object
  com.g6pay.sdk.G6Pay
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.g6pay.sdk.G6AdvertiserIF, com.g6pay.sdk.G6PublisherIF
public class G6Pay
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.g6pay.sdk.G6AdvertiserIF, com.g6pay.sdk.G6PublisherIF

The G6 Pay SDK. This class provides all the methods for interacting with a user's account, etc. 

 Sample install confirm:
 
        G6Pay sdk = G6Pay.getG6PayInstance(this.getApplicationContext());

        sdk.installConfirm();


 Sample offerwall showing:
 
        G6Pay sdk = G6Pay.getG6PayInstance(this.getApplicationContext());

        G6OfferListener listener = new G6OfferListener() {
            public void offerWasCompleted(OfferDTO offer) {
                // handle offer completion (implement this yourself)
                offerCompleted(offer);
            }
        };

        sdk.showOffers(this.getApplicationContext(), "USERIDHERE", listener);

 
 Notes:
See appropriate Listener classes for how to receive notifications of events.

Author:
Peter Hsu - silversc3@yahoo.com
See Also:
G6OfferListener, G6TransactionListener, G6UserAccountListener
